      <body>
         <head type="metadata"><name type="person" corresp="#SSC">Stillman S. Conant?</name> to <addressee><name type="person" key="#SLC">SLC</name></addressee>
               <date when="1884-03-31">31 March 1884</date> &#x2022; <name type="place">Washington, D. C.</name>
               <sourceline>(MS: CU-MARK, UCLC 41973)</sourceline>
            </head>
            <div1  type="letter">
               <pb xml:id="pb001" n="1" facs="conant01.jpg"/>
               <opener>
               <dateline rend="indentdateline">
                  <name type="place">Brooklyn</name> <date when="1884-03-31">Mch 31 /84</date></dateline>
                  <lb/><name type="person">Se침or Don Samuel Clemens&#8212;</name>
                  <lb/><name type="place"><space extent="2"/>Hartford</name>
               
                  <salute rend="noindent">Muy Se침or mio&#8212;</salute>
            </opener>
               <p rend="text-indent:2">He emprendido un viage desde un Pais muy lejano, lleno
               de peligros y vicisitudes, con el solo objeto de dirigirle hoy esta carta,
               y rogarle me mando su autografo para conservarlo en esta vida y en la venidera
               en la p치gina mas prominente de mi album.</p>
               <p rend="text-indent:2">Esperando no desatender치 mi peticion, soy de ud,<note type="an" place="foot" xml:id="an001" n="1">
                  Translated, with the help of Melissa Martin of the Mark Twain Project: "I embarked on a journey from a very distant place
                  full of hazards and vicissitudes, with the sole purpose of sending this letter to you today,
                  and I beg that you send your autograph, to conserve it in this life and in the next
                  in the most prominent page of my album. I hope that you will not disregard this request." S. S. Q. B. S. M. stands for Seguros Servidores Que Besan Sus Manos ("I remain very truly yours").</note></p>
                  <closer>
                     <salute rend="indentcompclose">S. S. Q. B. S. M.
                  </salute>
                     <signed rend="indentsig">Quixote de la Mancha</signed>
                  </closer>
                  <p rend="text-indent:2"><name type="place">22 Willow St
                  <lb/><space extent="4"/>Brooklyn
                     <lb/><space extent="5"/>N. Y.</name></p>
               
            </div1>
            
            <div1 type="post-transmission">
               <div2 type="envelope">
                  
               <pb xml:id="pb002" n="2" facs="conant-env.jpg"/>
